request.description: This api is used to validate the user and in return will give an access token along with other parameters.This access token will be used for all future API calls.Input here username and password in the body part.

This api is used to get the patient demographic information. The access token received in the previous api call should be used here.
This api is used to get the patient encounter information by the selected date. The access token received in the previous api call should be used here and the selected date as well.
This api is used to get the patient encounter information by the selected date range. The access token received in the previous api call should be used here and the selected date range as well.
